Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
-
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- Fixed problem causing calls to create/edit/view render functions for the 
  directories to be issued twice
- Fixed bug with multi schema support for directories: if several schemas are
  defined on some directory, they are merged into a transient dict instance at
  runtime
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- added schemas and schemas_search tokens properties to make it easier for
  extension profiles to register new schemas for directories without
  overwritting existing schemas
